<Base
  title="About ListingDescGen — Free Real Estate Listing Description Generator"
  description="ListingDescGen is a free template-based tool that helps real estate agents generate professional MLS-ready listing descriptions in seconds. No signup, no fees."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-violet prose-lg">
    <h1>About ListingDescGen</h1>
    <p>ListingDescGen is a free tool that helps real estate agents and sellers generate professional, MLS-ready listing descriptions in seconds. Enter your property details — beds, baths, features — and get a polished description instantly.</p>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>The generator uses professionally written templates tuned for each property type and tone (Professional, Warm &amp; Inviting, Luxury, Investment-focused). Select your tone, fill in the property details, and choose up to 3 key features to highlight. The tool assembles a ready-to-use description you can copy directly into your MLS system.</p>
    <h2>Who It's For</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Real estate agents who write dozens of listings per month</li>
      <li>FSBO (For Sale By Owner) sellers writing their first listing</li>
      <li>Property managers creating rental ads</li>
      <li>Investors describing fix-and-flip or buy-and-hold properties</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>All generation happens in your browser. We don't store property details or generated descriptions on our servers. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>
    <p>Questions? <a href="/contact/">Contact us</a> or email <a href="mailto:hello@listing-description-gen.com">hello@listing-description-gen.com</a></p>
  </div>
</Base>
